1
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:05,370
Episode 20

2
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:44,120
What are you doing here? When did you get here?

3
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:47,140
What about you, Conductor?

4
00:01:15,470 --> 00:01:20,600
If you were coming this way, you should have told me. It would have been nice to come together.

5
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:23,230
I wasn't planning to come before.

6
00:01:23,230 --> 00:01:26,480
But you still came.

7
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,740
Be comfortable. You came to see Jang Yun.

8
00:02:13,370 --> 00:02:17,130
If you won't look at him properly, why did you even come?

9
00:02:17,130 --> 00:02:20,300
I don't know, myself.

10
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:26,740
Just... I wanted to see him, even just for a moment.

11
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:31,330
You're quite frustrating. If I were you, I would have gone in as soon as I arrived.

12
00:02:31,330 --> 00:02:36,630
You came right after we went our separate ways, you must have wanted to see him so badly.

13
00:02:40,730 --> 00:02:42,510
I'm sorry.

14
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:45,370
Wow, that hurts my pride.

15
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:55,760
The truth is, I made up my mind

16
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,940
to not date him.

17
00:03:00,290 --> 00:03:04,870
Why would you decide that? You said you liked him.

18
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:07,180
It's because I like him.

19
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:15,750
I'm afraid of causing him harm because I like him.

20
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:18,440
What kind of excuse is that?

21
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:22,850
So does that mean I have some chance?

22
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,900
I better put in  more effort.

23
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:20,110
♪ Brilliant day

24
00:04:20,110 --> 00:04:26,010
♪ That day, beautiful day

25
00:04:57,090 --> 00:05:01,580
♫ can't you see it? ♫

26
00:05:01,580 --> 00:05:06,430
♫ can't you see it? ♫

27
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:11,600
♫ that heart-fluttering day, that day ♫

28
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:15,220
♫ beautiful day ♫

29
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:22,240
♫ my heart trembled so much ♫

30
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:26,610
♫ my heart beat so much ♫

31
00:05:26,610 --> 00:05:31,990
♫ that brilliant day, that day ♫

32
00:05:31,990 --> 00:05:35,030
♫ beautiful day ♫

33
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:41,830
♫ on that happy day, I'm loving you ♫

34
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:45,410
♫ to be loving you ♫

35
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:49,990
♫ I'm gonna love with you ♫

36
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:21,790
Yi Yeong

37
00:06:21,790 --> 00:06:25,520
What is it, in the middle of the night?

38
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,490
What is it?

39
00:06:36,990 --> 00:06:39,540
Yi Yeong, what's wrong?

40
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:41,900
What's wrong? Has something happened?

41
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:45,520
Why are you crying here? Are you hurt somewhere?

42
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:49,180
No...

43
00:06:51,570 --> 00:06:55,160
Please let me sleep in your room, Unni.

44
00:06:56,450 --> 00:06:59,600
I just can't go home.

45
00:07:03,050 --> 00:07:08,920
If I go home, I feel like I will go to his home instead.

46
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:15,150
His home is right down the stairs.

47
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:20,220
I feel like I can't hold myself back from going there.

48
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:25,000
Good for you for coming here. Good job.

49
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,180
Don't cry.

50
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:51,020
Try to sleep. I'll explain it to Mom and Dad somehow.

51
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:52,370
Okay.

52
00:08:01,550 --> 00:08:07,060
Please keep it for me, Unni. Please hide it for me.

53
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:10,200
Don't give it to me even if I ask for it.

54
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,800
Why are you going so far?

55
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:15,510
Alright.

56
00:08:44,430 --> 00:08:46,090
Here to practice?

57
00:08:46,090 --> 00:08:48,520
Yes.

58
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:50,690
You're practicing until late, too.

59
00:08:50,690 --> 00:08:52,570
The performance is right around the corner.

60
00:08:52,570 --> 00:08:54,210
Then, work hard.

61
00:08:54,210 --> 00:08:56,390
Do you want one?

62
00:08:58,330 --> 00:09:00,150
Me?

63
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:02,600
Yes.

64
00:09:05,170 --> 00:09:09,950
Well, then maybe just one can?

65
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:15,440
It's still cool.

66
00:09:18,530 --> 00:09:21,990
But why are you here, like this?

67
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:28,760
Just... feeling a little frustrated. You can speak to me casually.

68
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:32,970
Shall I?

69
00:09:32,970 --> 00:09:37,360
Today, you seem different from other days.

70
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:39,850
How am I usually?

71
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:42,040
Rude, of course.

72
00:09:46,570 --> 00:09:52,630
Well, I'm a bit rude myself, so I can't criticize.

73
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:55,670
But ... are you worried about something?

74
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:59,150
Piano? Or money?

75
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,240
So, love life, huh?

76
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:09,290
Well, just...

77
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:14,290
There is a woman I like,

78
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:17,490
but everything is so hard.

79
00:10:17,490 --> 00:10:22,150
This is the first time in my life I confessed my feelings.

80
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:26,360
But things aren't working out the way I thought.

81
00:10:31,290 --> 00:10:34,480
I don't know what the situation is,

82
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:39,600
but since I've lived a few more years than you, let me act as if I know something.

83
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:42,930
There isn't anything that works out as you thought.

84
00:10:42,930 --> 00:10:45,260
Especially when it comes to love.

85
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:50,100
Of course there are some lucky guys.

86
00:10:50,100 --> 00:10:55,610
But people with bad luck, like me ... we have to prepare ourselves.

87
00:10:55,610 --> 00:10:57,040
Prepare?

88
00:10:57,040 --> 00:11:00,990
Yes, prepare to be punished.

89
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:09,470
To tell you a secret, I'm a married man.

90
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:14,370
I have a wife and child in the U.S. My daughter is eight years old.

91
00:11:14,370 --> 00:11:17,950
It's been five years since I've seen my daughter.

92
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:20,170
Five years since I've separated from my wife.

93
00:11:20,170 --> 00:11:23,290
We haven't divorced yet due to circumstances

94
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:26,910
and I'm working myself ragged to send child support payments.

95
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:32,210
But I'm also dating someone.

96
00:11:34,550 --> 00:11:37,630
I'm sure I will be punished someday.

97
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:39,790
I'm prepared for it.

98
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:50,610
Without even preparing for punishment, how can I begin such a difficult love?

99
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:52,940
It's not a joke, after all.

100
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:12,670
Imagine that Conductor would summon me here? Gosh, if you live long enough, you see all sorts of things.

101
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:14,920
What were you thinking working at that flower shop?

102
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:19,910
I have to make a living, and there are things to find out.

103
00:12:21,890 --> 00:12:24,330
You leave that alone, I will take care of Hong Yi Yeong.

104
00:12:24,330 --> 00:12:28,750
I don't care what happens to Hong Yi Yeong.

105
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:32,020
I just need to find what's mine.

106
00:12:32,950 --> 00:12:36,030
Isn't it the same for you, Conductor?

107
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,890
Maybe not?

108
00:12:41,890 --> 00:12:46,860
Were you the one who told Professor Kang about C.E.O. Jang?

109
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:54,960
I do whatever gets me paid.

110
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:59,250
What is your purpose, really? It is really just money?

111
00:12:59,250 --> 00:13:03,560
I told you, it's revenge. Why do you keep forgetting that?

112
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:05,480
You know you guys put me in jail.

113
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:08,180
But you offered to do it.

114
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:15,840
I did it because you offered me money. And you didn't even pay me all of it.

115
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,760
Have you forgotten?

116
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:22,700
But why did you do that, that day?

117
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:29,230
If only you hadn't gotten involved, that unlucky accident wouldn't have happened.

118
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:34,470
It was because of you, Conductor, that Kim Ian died that day.

119
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:39,400
Be careful of what you say. What do you know, anyway?

120
00:13:40,190 --> 00:13:42,910
Be careful.

121
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:46,500
If you don't want to rot in jail like I did.

122
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:13,500
- Isn't that pretty?
- It is.

123
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:16,690
It grew so much.

124
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:20,050
She's not here because something happened, really?

125
00:15:20,050 --> 00:15:24,130
Yi Yeong? I told you, nothing is going on.

126
00:15:24,130 --> 00:15:26,820
She just came because she missed father.

127
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:28,540
She's so grown up, and in the middle of the night?

128
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:32,490
Mom, really. Is there a right time to miss someone?

129
00:15:32,490 --> 00:15:36,010
You can't even date, but your mouth is alive.

130
00:15:36,010 --> 00:15:40,220
She just looks so much thinner in just one day.

131
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:42,350
Let's have breakfast.

132
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:47,040
Honey, Yi Yeong wants to stay a few more days.

133
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:49,200
How nice for you, Honey.

134
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:56,320
After work, I'll pack some things and come back here.

135
00:15:57,710 --> 00:16:01,580
Wow, rice for breakfast. How long has it been?

136
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:09,360
Will you really be alright? If you go to work, you'll run into him.

137
00:16:10,430 --> 00:16:14,930
I know where he usually goes, so I can avoid him.

138
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,660
Unni,

139
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:26,070
I'm thinking of quitting Sinyeong Philharmonic.

140
00:16:26,070 --> 00:16:28,880
What are you saying, out of the blue?

141
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:31,530
You practiced for years trying to get into that orchestra.

142
00:16:31,530 --> 00:16:35,370
What about your promise to my father, that you will let him see you perform?

143
00:16:38,590 --> 00:16:41,550
I can't play anymore.

144
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:46,070
I can't hold the mallet, I feel too ashamed.

145
00:16:46,070 --> 00:16:47,880
But why would you feel like that?

146
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:51,500
You've worked so hard for fifteen years, without any rest.

147
00:16:54,220 --> 00:16:58,890
You silly, if you think you killed someone, how can you play?

148
00:16:58,890 --> 00:17:01,260
But you didn't stab him yourself, I told you so many times.

149
00:17:01,260 --> 00:17:03,960
I told you to forget about it.

150
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:07,290
But I did stab him, Unni.

151
00:17:07,290 --> 00:17:10,030
I even remember that scene.

152
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:17,320
What are you saying, Yi Yeong?

153
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:23,410
Who stabbed whom?

154
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:24,590
Auntie...

155
00:17:24,590 --> 00:17:26,600
It's nothing, Mom, you misheard us.

156
00:17:26,600 --> 00:17:28,660
Hurry and leave, please.

157
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:37,390
Hurry and tell me.

158
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:41,910
What you two said, what does it mean?

159
00:17:41,910 --> 00:17:44,410
Who killed whom?

160
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:46,900
Mom, let me explain.

161
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:48,830
I will explain, so please leave.

162
00:17:48,830 --> 00:17:51,500
Yi Yeong, go to work now. Quick!

163
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:34,990
Sinyeong Philharmonic Orchestra, A Night of Encouragement
Tonight at 7
Orchestra Rehearsal Room

164
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:37,390
Concertmaster and all the section leaders

165
00:18:37,390 --> 00:18:40,320
must make sure to attend the Encouragement.

166
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:43,560
We will greet a new board member today.

167
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:48,690
Concertmaster, you're performing tonight? Since you're doing it, make sure to surprise everyone.

168
00:18:48,690 --> 00:18:50,480
Why must I do that?

169
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:53,290
The new board member especially loves the violin.

170
00:18:53,290 --> 00:18:56,580
Who knows? Maybe he'll offer you support?

171
00:18:56,580 --> 00:18:58,850
No way.

172
00:19:09,150 --> 00:19:11,770
I brought the clothes from the cleaners'.

173
00:19:11,770 --> 00:19:13,930
You should try them on.

174
00:19:13,930 --> 00:19:17,850
No need, I've worn them all before.

175
00:19:17,850 --> 00:19:20,840
What will you do? We can go together.

176
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:22,980
No, how can I go there?

177
00:19:22,980 --> 00:19:26,450
It's a meeting for checking each other out.

178
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:31,410
I really don't want to go.

179
00:19:31,410 --> 00:19:35,530
If you tell me not to go, I will call you "noona".

180
00:19:35,530 --> 00:19:39,200
I don't want to be your noona, Conductor.

181
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:44,950
The day after tomorrow is your performance to celebrate your appointment. You can't be so lethargic.

182
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:47,800
You have to be strong. Strong.

183
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:00,080
Just ten seconds, please.

184
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:03,690
Then I can forget about all the bad stuff and just go, I think.

185
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:27,860
A Night of Encouragement

186
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:32,360
Professor Kang

187
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:53,550
What are you doing?

188
00:20:59,290 --> 00:21:01,930
Am I a virus that you're avoiding?

189
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:06,410
Hiding here and there, you thought I wouldn't notice?

190
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:13,290
You didn't come home last night. What happened to your cell phone, did you throw it away?

191
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:16,090
I don't use cell phones anymore.

192
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:20,890
I thought I would go completely crazy yesterday.

193
00:21:20,890 --> 00:21:24,300
Every minute, every second, when is Yi Yeong coming, and why is her phone turned off?

194
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:28,610
Trying to call you again, coming out here to look for you.

195
00:21:28,610 --> 00:21:31,940
♫ you are swayed like a wave ♫

196
00:21:31,940 --> 00:21:35,540
♫ Being with you ♫

197
00:21:35,540 --> 00:21:39,980
Even if you don't want to, please hear me out for a moment.

198
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:44,370
♫ I can never get tired ♫

199
00:21:44,370 --> 00:21:46,760
I haven't decided to end this.

200
00:21:46,760 --> 00:21:50,630
I've also decided not to torment myself by imagining any bad scenarios, as you did.

201
00:21:50,630 --> 00:21:53,170
Of course, things can get pretty bad for us, worse than now.

202
00:21:53,170 --> 00:21:55,260
Other people may criticize us.

203
00:21:55,260 --> 00:21:58,120
But

204
00:21:58,120 --> 00:22:02,590
I'm 100% sincere towards you, Yi Yeong,

205
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:06,690
so I'm not afraid of anything that might come our way.

206
00:22:06,690 --> 00:22:11,010
So I'll just let it come, whatever it may be.

207
00:22:11,010 --> 00:22:14,620
♫ So that I can love you more ♫

208
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:16,240
♫ for a long time ♫

209
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:18,320
But you will still keep hiding, won't you?
♫ what I treasure it alone ♫

210
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:21,390
♫ Before this feeling wanes ♫

211
00:22:21,390 --> 00:22:25,970
I don't mind you hiding, but please let me know where you are.

212
00:22:25,970 --> 00:22:27,020
♫ so that I won't get weary ♫

213
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:31,590
So I can come to see you when I miss you. I'll be going now.

214
00:22:38,010 --> 00:22:42,750
♫ You take me all ♫

215
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:51,570
My father never scolded, ever since I was young.

216
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:55,040
- He's the best.
- Is that right?

217
00:22:55,040 --> 00:22:57,760
Have you come to see me perform?

218
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:04,280
Why did she come here? Now I see that she looks just like her father.

219
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:08,330
To be honest, rather than Hong Yi Yeong, isn't she our worst musician?

220
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:09,800
Even worse, for a long time.

221
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:14,130
Of course, with the board's backing ... Her father is the Chairwoman's classmate.

222
00:23:14,130 --> 00:23:15,770
Isn't that right?

223
00:23:15,770 --> 00:23:18,350
Classmate, then they are the same age?

224
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:20,390
Is he old enough to be her uncle?

225
00:23:22,770 --> 00:23:26,490
Assistant Yang, what about Maestro Nam? He didn't escape somewhere, did he?

226
00:23:26,490 --> 00:23:30,340
No, I saw him in his office a short while ago. He said he is coming.

227
00:23:31,210 --> 00:23:34,120
Please call Jang Yun, and Maestro Nam, too.

228
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:35,670
Yes.

229
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:51,050
You're here, Chairwoman?

230
00:23:54,330 --> 00:23:55,800
Madame.

231
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:58,080
Hello, hello.

232
00:23:58,080 --> 00:23:59,220
Hello.

233
00:23:59,220 --> 00:24:01,380
Oh hello, you've come?

234
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:03,400
Hello. Hello.

235
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,150
How nice to see you, please sit.

236
00:24:05,150 --> 00:24:06,680
Yes.

237
00:24:26,220 --> 00:24:30,170
C.E.O. Jang, it has been a long time.

238
00:24:30,910 --> 00:24:32,620
Yes.

239
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:50,980
Welcome, C.E.O.

240
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:53,400
Oh, Manager Yun.

241
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,910
You look pretty today.

242
00:25:00,910 --> 00:25:03,630
Thank you, you too, Manager Yun.

243
00:25:04,390 --> 00:25:07,960
The Chairmwoman was just talking about you.

244
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:12,280
C.E.O. Jang, oh, hello.

245
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:15,030
You look so great today.

246
00:25:22,700 --> 00:25:25,320
- Come this way.
- Yes.

247
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:36,220
Isn't he the new board member?

248
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:40,160
Ha Eun Ju, you can't beat her.

249
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:43,470
I once did. There were times like that.

250
00:25:43,470 --> 00:25:45,760
That one, really...

251
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:53,570
Unni, has Auntie come to my place, by any chance?

252
00:25:53,570 --> 00:25:57,630
Yes, Mom went to pack all your things this afternoon.

253
00:25:57,630 --> 00:26:00,260
She won't let you stay there, she said.

254
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:04,630
She couldn't open the flower shop today. She cried all day long.

255
00:26:04,630 --> 00:26:06,500
Is she crying, even now?

256
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:07,760
Not anymore.

257
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:10,780
She doesn't let it show in front of Father. Hurry and come home.

258
00:26:10,780 --> 00:26:14,460
Yeah, I will.

259
00:26:29,210 --> 00:26:32,020
Did you kill Ian, Conductor?

260
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:38,380
If only you hadn't gotten involved, that unlucky accident wouldn't have happened.

261
00:26:42,120 --> 00:26:45,190
Do you really not remember this knife?

262
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:48,400
It's the knife that Ian was stabbed with.

263
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:51,160
It was because of you, Conductor,

264
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:55,060
that Kim Ian died that day.

265
00:26:55,060 --> 00:26:59,290
Yang Su Jeong

266
00:27:24,550 --> 00:27:27,210
You asked me yesterday

267
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:31,110
why I'm keeping Yi Yeong by my side.

268
00:27:31,110 --> 00:27:33,860
I thought about that all day

269
00:27:35,290 --> 00:27:39,820
and it's because I like her. I realized that, thanks to you.

270
00:27:58,630 --> 00:28:00,600
Excuse me?

271
00:28:07,730 --> 00:28:09,770
Who are you?

272
00:28:14,980 --> 00:28:16,600
Hello.

273
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:20,250
We met yesterday. I work here part-time.

274
00:28:22,810 --> 00:28:27,210
But why are you here at this time? Did Auntie ask you to come?

275
00:28:27,210 --> 00:28:32,140
It's not that. I just left something behind during work today.

276
00:28:37,130 --> 00:28:38,980
Today?

277
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:45,280
Oh, right, today the shop was closed.

278
00:28:52,500 --> 00:28:53,860
Oh, so much?

279
00:28:53,860 --> 00:28:55,160
Thank you.

280
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:58,070
Yes, I will eat it well.

281
00:28:58,070 --> 00:28:59,180
I apologize.

282
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:01,350
Thank you.

283
00:29:06,800 --> 00:29:09,880
It's been a long time, Miss Hong Yi Yeong.

284
00:29:33,260 --> 00:29:35,390
Don't come!

285
00:29:44,010 --> 00:29:46,140
Please don't come!

286
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:49,670
We meet again, Miss Hong Yi Yeong.

287
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:53,010
It's been a long time.

288
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:58,910
Ahjussi, you chased me like this last year, didn't you?

289
00:31:02,860 --> 00:31:05,920
The day Kim Ian died...

290
00:31:08,410 --> 00:31:11,030
you were the one who came after me. Right?

291
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:29,760
Timing and Subtitles by the Sing To Me Team @ viki

292
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:35,520
♫ Because I can't forget, I cry. ♫

293
00:31:36,810 --> 00:31:42,370
♫ Even if it is a lie, I I try ♫

294
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:47,530
♫ Why am I still looking for you here? ♫

295
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:50,430
♫ While I'm looking for you who won't come ♫
